## Extending the stack

To add a new service:

1. Drop a fresh compose fragment under `docker/compose/<service>.yaml`.
2. Add it to the `include:` list in `compose.yaml`.
3. (Optional) Add a route to `docker/envoy/envoy.yaml`.
4. (Optional) Add env vars to `.env.example`.

For a more structured approach, see `.cursor/rules/extending-the-stack.md`.

